1
00:01:21,350 --> 00:01:26,910
[A Splendid Match]

2
00:01:27,500 --> 00:01:29,780
[Episode 27]

3
00:01:30,710 --> 00:01:32,370
When a nation is about to fall,

4
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:35,840
traitors like you always appear.

5
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,759
I'm willing to risk my life

6
00:01:39,789 --> 00:01:41,380
to purge you rom our land.

7
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:46,200
Marquis Changxing's spirit

8
00:01:46,220 --> 00:01:48,140
is truly formidable.

9
00:01:48,759 --> 00:01:49,710
But don't forget

10
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:52,789
that your son is still in my hands.

11
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,130
If you're not afraid

12
00:01:59,509 --> 00:02:01,760
of leaving your line without an heir,

13
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:04,000
then go ahead and take my head.

14
00:02:04,030 --> 00:02:04,880
You!

15
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:15,940
Do it.

16
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,310
My Lord.

17
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,710
Ye Xian suddenly fell ill.

18
00:02:24,710 --> 00:02:25,890
It doesn't look good.

19
00:02:25,890 --> 00:02:27,290
What have you done to him?

20
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,620
Go check on him now.

21
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:37,620
[Marquis of Changxing's Signed Confession]

22
00:02:45,970 --> 00:02:46,370
This...

23
00:02:46,370 --> 00:02:46,829
This...

24
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:52,620
He's still breathing.

25
00:02:52,620 --> 00:02:53,530
Fetch a physician immediately.

26
00:02:53,530 --> 00:02:54,000
My Lord.

27
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:56,910
Ye Xian is still Marquis Changxing's heir.

28
00:02:56,910 --> 00:02:57,829
If anything happens to him,

29
00:02:57,829 --> 00:02:59,560
I'm afraid His Majesty
will hold us accountable.

30
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,750
The Penal Court can't shoulder this blame.

31
00:03:00,750 --> 00:03:02,400
Well, then report it to the court.

32
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:02,910
Yes!

33
00:03:10,190 --> 00:03:11,520
Take the pill.

34
00:03:26,940 --> 00:03:27,800
I'll make sure Ye Xian

35
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,800
takes the poison.

36
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:32,000
It'll force his blood
to circulate violently

37
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,530
and trigger a heart attack.

38
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,050
When it happens,

39
00:03:35,620 --> 00:03:37,430
you go in under the excuse
of checking on him,

40
00:03:37,430 --> 00:03:38,890
and give him the antidote.

41
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:41,710
As long as he receives it in time,

42
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:43,510
it won't do much harm to his body.

43
00:03:54,910 --> 00:03:55,560
My Lady.

44
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:56,520
My Lady.

45
00:03:56,910 --> 00:03:58,190
Qingpu, how is it?

46
00:04:00,470 --> 00:04:01,030
My Lady.

47
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,000
Young Lord Ye...

48
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,240
and the Marquis have both been released,

49
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:07,150
and returned to the Marquis's Mansion.

50
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:08,080
Thank goodness.

51
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,430
Wait.

52
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,660
If they're already back home,

53
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:15,780
then I don't need to visit him myself.

54
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,620
I'll ask Fifth Aunt

55
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,940
to pass it along for me.

56
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:21,529
Let's go.

57
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,390
Ye,

58
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:28,320
if you walk out of this Gu Mansion today,

59
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:30,040
don't think about coming back!

60
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:30,880
So be it.

61
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:33,060
I don't care about this place anyway.

62
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,560
Dismissed.

63
00:04:39,860 --> 00:04:41,320
Whether you like it or not,

64
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:42,520
you're not leaving.

65
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:44,630
Today, within this mansion,

66
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:45,760
not a single person,

67
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,390
high or low,

68
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,120
no one can leave the mansion

69
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,450
without my permission.

70
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,040
You...

71
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,840
Grandmother.

72
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,510
You're trying this hard to stop her—

73
00:04:53,510 --> 00:04:54,770
does that mean you're certain

74
00:04:54,770 --> 00:04:56,480
that the Senior Grand Secretary
would bring down Marquis Changxing,

75
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:58,000
and the Gu family'd be implicated as well?

76
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:58,530
Exactly.

77
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:00,560
That is a matter

78
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,980
of life and death,

79
00:05:02,310 --> 00:05:03,600
so we can't afford to be careless.

80
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,920
But have you considered what happens

81
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:06,980
if the Senior Grand Secretary fails?

82
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,720
How many military generals in Great Yan

83
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,450
once served under the Marquis?

84
00:05:11,750 --> 00:05:13,070
Now that the Marquis is in trouble,

85
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:14,360
we, as their relatives by marriage,

86
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,510
are actively stopping Fifth Aunt

87
00:05:15,510 --> 00:05:17,040
from returning home to support her family.

88
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,510
Forget how disgraceful it would look

89
00:05:18,510 --> 00:05:19,440
if word gets out.

90
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:22,160
If the Marquis family
ever recovers its footing

91
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,430
and decides to settle scores—

92
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:25,000
do you really think our family's status

93
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,190
is enough to withstand the revenge

94
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:28,050
of the entire military nobility?

95
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,650
What do you mean?

96
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,000
Did Lord Chen

97
00:05:32,159 --> 00:05:33,690
tell you the Marquis family

98
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,970
would come through this unharmed?

99
00:05:36,650 --> 00:05:38,580
He would never tell me such things.

100
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,040
But if you've been reading

101
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,920
the imperial bulletin lately, you'd know

102
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,690
the court's peace talks
with the Nothern Barbarians

103
00:05:43,690 --> 00:05:45,390
have been dragging on without result.

104
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:46,430
If the talks fail,

105
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:47,630
there will be war.

106
00:05:48,190 --> 00:05:49,650
And once war breaks out...

107
00:05:51,950 --> 00:05:52,830
If I were you,

108
00:05:53,310 --> 00:05:54,970
I would simply turn a blind eye

109
00:05:55,380 --> 00:05:57,070
and let Fifth Aunt
come and go as she pleases.

110
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:59,510
No matter what happens
to the Marquis family,

111
00:05:59,510 --> 00:06:00,680
if anyone questions us later,

112
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:02,080
we can stand firm and say,

113
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:03,800
"We're family by marriage.

114
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:04,720
Who wouldn't help

115
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,750
their own kin?"

116
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,430
Old Madam,

117
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,630
Marquis Changxing's Mansion men are here,

118
00:06:11,630 --> 00:06:12,940
saying Young Lord Ye

119
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,630
suffered a sudden heart attack in prison,

120
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:16,630
and the Marquis collapsed on the spot.

121
00:06:16,630 --> 00:06:18,950
They've been brought back
to the mansion for treatment.

122
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:20,310
Fifth Madam is requested

123
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:21,870
to go back and look after him.

124
00:06:21,870 --> 00:06:22,800
I'll go back right now.

125
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,870
I'll go back right away.

126
00:06:23,870 --> 00:06:24,530
Fifth Aunt,

127
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,290
you may take my carriage.

128
00:06:26,290 --> 00:06:27,220
I'll see you off.

129
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:27,960
Let's go.

130
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,000
Fifth Aunt.

131
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:44,560
there's something I need to tell you.

132
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,990
But you must promise me

133
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:48,050
not to breathe a word of it to anyone,

134
00:06:48,050 --> 00:06:49,190
including the Marquis

135
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:49,950
and his wife.

136
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:51,800
Otherwise,

137
00:06:52,830 --> 00:06:55,120
the whole Marquis family
will be in danger.

138
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,510
If it concerns the safety
of the Marquis family,

139
00:06:56,510 --> 00:06:57,510
I won't say a word.

140
00:06:59,070 --> 00:06:59,950
Actually,

141
00:07:01,190 --> 00:07:03,310
Ye Xian's heart attack wasn't a relapse,

142
00:07:03,310 --> 00:07:05,040
but was induced with medicine,

143
00:07:05,390 --> 00:07:06,540
intentionally.

144
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,630
Because it was the only way

145
00:07:08,630 --> 00:07:10,230
to get the Marquis released.

146
00:07:11,270 --> 00:07:13,670
His Majesty wants
to save Marquis Changxing,

147
00:07:13,670 --> 00:07:15,930
but doesn't dare openly defy the mentor.

148
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,950
And with the Marquis Changxing's temper,

149
00:07:17,950 --> 00:07:19,720
even under torture,

150
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,970
he'd never yield and beg for mercy.

151
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:22,830
He might even

152
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:27,130
say something treacherous

153
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,930
that would only worsen his situation.

154
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:30,920
So,

155
00:07:31,430 --> 00:07:32,720
the only option was to rely on Ye Xian—

156
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,510
to have him enter prison with his father.

157
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:35,120
That way,

158
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,870
Marquis Changxing would think of his son

159
00:07:37,870 --> 00:07:39,110
and wouldn't be so stubborn.

160
00:07:39,110 --> 00:07:40,440
Once Ye Xian collapsed,

161
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,420
Marquis Changxing

162
00:07:42,580 --> 00:07:43,850
would have no choice but to yield,

163
00:07:43,850 --> 00:07:45,360
which would give His Majesty an excuse

164
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,620
to plead on his behalf.

165
00:08:02,510 --> 00:08:03,390
It seems

166
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,890
the pill prepared
by the Marquis's Mansion worked.

167
00:08:05,890 --> 00:08:07,220
His pulse is stable now.

168
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:09,390
It's just that His Lordship's

169
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,510
long illness,

170
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:12,810
combined with his time in prison,

171
00:08:12,870 --> 00:08:14,940
has taken a severe toll on his body.

172
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:16,510
He needs proper care.

173
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:17,680
I will write a prescription.

174
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:20,480
Have him take it for half a month
and see how it goes.

175
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,570
Thank you for your trouble.

176
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,330
This way.

177
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,400
Thanks for your trouble.

178
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,120
My Lady,

179
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,720
Fifth Madam has arrived.

180
00:08:48,870 --> 00:08:49,530
Fifth Aunt.

181
00:08:50,150 --> 00:08:50,790
How is he?

182
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,240
He's taken the medicine.

183
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,080
The imperial physician said

184
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,410
his pulse is stable now.

185
00:08:57,550 --> 00:08:58,680
That's good to hear.

186
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:06,280
Xian is blessed by heaven—

187
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,440
he made it through,

188
00:09:07,870 --> 00:09:09,730
and brought Father home with him.

189
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:10,510
Right.

190
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:14,260
Thank heavens and the bodhisattvas.

191
00:09:18,270 --> 00:09:20,310
Has Miss Gu left yet?

192
00:09:21,670 --> 00:09:23,130
She wouldn't come inside,

193
00:09:23,390 --> 00:09:25,120
and I didn't dare invite her in.

194
00:09:25,510 --> 00:09:27,330
If Xian sees her,

195
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,600
it'll only cause another scene.

196
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,590
Gu Jinzhao.

197
00:09:33,910 --> 00:09:34,950
Gu Jinzhao.

198
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:35,740
Gu Jin...

199
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,120
-Xian.
-Xian!

200
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:39,720
Xian.

201
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:40,990
Xian.

202
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,770
Is Gu Jinzhao here?

203
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,240
Where is she?

204
00:09:44,270 --> 00:09:45,800
You can't get out of bed yet.

205
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:46,870
Where is she?

206
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,120
Let her in.

207
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:49,910
-I have something to ask her.
-Don't do this, Xian!

208
00:09:49,910 --> 00:09:50,360
Xian!

209
00:09:50,550 --> 00:09:50,960
Xian!

210
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:53,620
Mother, don't stop him.

211
00:09:53,620 --> 00:09:54,470
Let him go.

212
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,700
Zhao is waiting outside the door.

213
00:09:56,790 --> 00:09:57,510
If you don't care

214
00:09:57,510 --> 00:09:58,360
about this family anymore

215
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,510
and want to piss your parents to death,

216
00:09:59,510 --> 00:10:00,890
then go find her!

217
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:03,750
But even if you go out there—

218
00:10:03,750 --> 00:10:04,600
what then?

219
00:10:05,630 --> 00:10:07,150
Zhao would rather wait at the door

220
00:10:07,150 --> 00:10:08,340
than step inside.

221
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:10,730
Don't you understand what that means?

222
00:10:11,630 --> 00:10:13,530
Even if you won't think of us,

223
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:15,630
at least think of her.

224
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:18,240
Xian,

225
00:10:19,510 --> 00:10:20,750
I'm begging you.

226
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:24,500
For the sake of our old and frail parents,

227
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:26,030
and me, a married daughter

228
00:10:26,030 --> 00:10:27,600
who's utterly powerless—

229
00:10:28,910 --> 00:10:31,120
please stop chasing after Zhao.

230
00:10:31,750 --> 00:10:32,960
Stop making a scene,

231
00:10:32,980 --> 00:10:33,980
will you?

232
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:37,440
Xian,

233
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:39,080
I'm begging you.

234
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,620
Just listen to your sister.

235
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:42,870
Our family

236
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:44,630
cannot take any more of this.

237
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:52,910
Xian.

238
00:10:53,030 --> 00:10:53,790
I know.

239
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,320
I won't go to her.

240
00:10:59,910 --> 00:11:00,910
You may leave now.

241
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:03,670
Leave!

242
00:12:15,270 --> 00:12:17,560
As soon as I heard that Ye Xian's
heart condition had relapsed

243
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:19,870
and Marquis Changxing had
coughed up blood on the spot,

244
00:12:19,870 --> 00:12:20,790
I was so anxious

245
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:23,510
that I had them both sent back

246
00:12:23,510 --> 00:12:25,170
to the mansion for treatment.

247
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,390
Looking back now,

248
00:12:26,510 --> 00:12:27,640
it was rather hasty.

249
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,760
I hope you can forgive me, Mr. Fu.

250
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:34,030
Your Majesty overstates the matter.

251
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:37,280
[Honor and Illumination]

252
00:12:35,270 --> 00:12:37,540
Your Majesty is kind and generous.

253
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,510
It's truly a blessing for Great Yan.

254
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:41,370
It's just that Marquis Changxing

255
00:12:41,630 --> 00:12:43,680
has always been arrogant

256
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:44,840
and obstinate.

257
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,200
Your Majesty

258
00:12:46,670 --> 00:12:48,530
alawys treats him with kindness,

259
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:49,840
but he

260
00:12:51,510 --> 00:12:52,960
fails to appreciate it.

261
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:57,880
Your Majesty,

262
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,240
Lord Chen Yanyun

263
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,840
is already waiting outside.

264
00:13:01,510 --> 00:13:02,200
Let him in.

265
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,460
Greetings, Your Majesty.

266
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:11,780
You may rise, Chen Yanyun.

267
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:14,760
Thank you, Your Majesty.

268
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,360
Grand Secretary.

269
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:19,850
Chen Yanyun,

270
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:22,200
I heard that

271
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:24,120
while interrogating Marquis Changxing,

272
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,780
you were nearly killed by him.

273
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:27,630
Thank you for your concern, Your Majesty,

274
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:29,270
but I didn't suffer any losses.

275
00:13:29,270 --> 00:13:30,670
Ye Xian spoke insolently

276
00:13:31,270 --> 00:13:32,670
and openly resisted arrest.

277
00:13:32,670 --> 00:13:33,200
And I

278
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:35,630
nearly strangled him to death.

279
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:38,560
Ye Xian has always been impulsive.

280
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:39,910
I've warned him so many times,

281
00:13:39,910 --> 00:13:41,110
yet he never listens.

282
00:13:41,270 --> 00:13:42,200
Both you and Ye Xian

283
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,990
are my most trusted ministers.

284
00:13:44,010 --> 00:13:45,530
Why let a moment of anger

285
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:47,310
escalate things this far?

286
00:13:47,550 --> 00:13:48,350
Your Majesty.

287
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:50,510
There is a limit to what a man can endure.

288
00:13:50,510 --> 00:13:52,170
Ye Xian ruined the reputation

289
00:13:52,270 --> 00:13:53,700
of my fiancée

290
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,750
and tried to assassinate me in the street.

291
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:56,630
I cannot

292
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:57,840
simply let that pass.

293
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:01,100
I ask for Your Majesty's understanding.

294
00:14:09,510 --> 00:14:10,960
Has Marquis Changxing

295
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,830
confessed yet?

296
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,300
Marquis Changxing

297
00:14:16,510 --> 00:14:18,510
had stubbornly refused to confess.

298
00:14:18,510 --> 00:14:21,960
But when he heard that Ye Xian
had suffered a sudden heart attack,

299
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:23,600
he coughed up blood on the spot.

300
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:25,390
After receiving Your Majesty's pardon,

301
00:14:25,390 --> 00:14:27,510
he returned
to Marquis Changxing's Mansion to recover.

302
00:14:27,510 --> 00:14:28,670
From his sickbed,

303
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:30,600
he wrote a memorial

304
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:32,620
and asked me

305
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:35,980
to present it to Your Majesty.

306
00:14:55,170 --> 00:14:56,220
[Ashamed to face my old friends, I beg
Your Majesty to strip me of my post]

307
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:57,760
[For the sake of my humble service,
please allow my bones to return home]

308
00:15:00,270 --> 00:15:02,870
Marquis Changxing's requesting retirement.

309
00:15:17,670 --> 00:15:19,990
It seems seeing Ye Xian so gravely ill

310
00:15:20,270 --> 00:15:21,870
has truly broken his spirit.

311
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:28,000
Your Majesty,

312
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:31,260
although Marquis Changxing
has requested retirement,

313
00:15:31,260 --> 00:15:33,660
he hasn't formally confess to the charges.

314
00:15:35,030 --> 00:15:36,630
Since you and Ye Xian are at odds,

315
00:15:36,630 --> 00:15:37,360
then for this case,

316
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:39,150
you should have recused yourself from it.

317
00:15:39,150 --> 00:15:39,950
Your Majesty.

318
00:15:40,910 --> 00:15:41,480
But...

319
00:15:44,510 --> 00:15:45,150
Yes.

320
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:47,910
Mr. Fu,

321
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:51,690
Marquis Changxing
has outstanding military achievements.

322
00:15:51,690 --> 00:15:52,870
When Prince Ruichang rebelled,

323
00:15:52,870 --> 00:15:54,390
he risked his life to defend the throne.

324
00:15:54,390 --> 00:15:56,270
He has made great contributions
to Great Yan.

325
00:15:56,270 --> 00:15:58,360
Perhaps, we can spare him this time?

326
00:16:04,270 --> 00:16:07,320
Since Your Majesty pleads
on Marquis Changxing's behalf,

327
00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:09,550
I shall obey the decree.

328
00:16:10,630 --> 00:16:12,890
However, the laws of the nation is clear.

329
00:16:13,290 --> 00:16:14,270
We cannot

330
00:16:15,270 --> 00:16:16,630
treat them too lightly.

331
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:25,000
Lord Chen,

332
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:27,510
when the imperial physician returned

333
00:16:27,510 --> 00:16:29,270
from the mansion, what did he say?

334
00:16:29,270 --> 00:16:30,270
Grand Secretary,

335
00:16:30,910 --> 00:16:32,390
during the previous palace coup,

336
00:16:32,390 --> 00:16:33,450
Marquis Changxing

337
00:16:34,030 --> 00:16:35,490
suffered severe injuries

338
00:16:35,630 --> 00:16:37,160
and never fully recovered.

339
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,390
Now, after with

340
00:16:38,550 --> 00:16:40,610
Young Lord Ye's sudden heart attack,

341
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:42,350
he coughed blood on the spot.

342
00:16:42,510 --> 00:16:44,150
His condition has worsened even more.

343
00:16:44,150 --> 00:16:45,750
The physician's assessment

344
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:49,260
was that the damage is irreversible.

345
00:16:50,750 --> 00:16:53,270
Irreversible?

346
00:17:05,410 --> 00:17:06,450
In that case,

347
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:09,099
we shall spare Marquis Changxing.

348
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:12,170
Mr. Fu, you're truly magnanimous!

349
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:13,200
Issue the decree.

350
00:17:13,550 --> 00:17:17,160
Considering Marquis Changxing's
past campaigns for the nation,

351
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,680
and his role in suppressing
the northern barbarians,

352
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:20,240
his contribution to the nation shall

353
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:22,440
offset his offense against the throne.

354
00:17:22,790 --> 00:17:24,240
I hope that the father and son

355
00:17:24,240 --> 00:17:25,829
will live up to my expectations

356
00:17:25,829 --> 00:17:27,290
and make no more mistakes.

357
00:17:28,349 --> 00:17:30,110
I hear and obey.

358
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:35,050
If Your Majesty wants

359
00:17:35,050 --> 00:17:36,910
to save Marquis Changxing's life

360
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:39,210
and his reputation,

361
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:41,300
then forgive me, I cannot do that.

362
00:17:41,790 --> 00:17:42,350
But...

363
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:44,600
if Your Majesty merely wants

364
00:17:44,750 --> 00:17:47,080
to save Marquis Changxing's reputation,

365
00:17:47,110 --> 00:17:48,710
then there may still be a way.

366
00:17:48,750 --> 00:17:49,310
It may be

367
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:50,760
worth trying.

368
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:52,220
What is it?

369
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,330
Make Marquis Changxing

370
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:56,330
understand the stakes.

371
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:58,410
Make him bow his head first,

372
00:17:58,510 --> 00:17:59,030
and

373
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:01,000
it must be genuine.

374
00:18:05,030 --> 00:18:05,960
Bow his head?

375
00:18:07,830 --> 00:18:09,490
Let alone Marquis Changxing,

376
00:18:10,270 --> 00:18:11,400
even I, the Emperor,

377
00:18:11,960 --> 00:18:13,490
must sometimes do the same.

378
00:18:17,390 --> 00:18:21,450
[Ji family's Silk Store]

379
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:19,920
His Majesty

380
00:18:20,270 --> 00:18:22,030
has pardoned Marquis Changxing's Mansion.

381
00:18:22,030 --> 00:18:23,240
So the Marquis Changxing

382
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:24,770
and his family are safe now?

383
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:25,750
Yes.

384
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:27,480
That's great.

385
00:18:28,110 --> 00:18:29,570
What a relief.

386
00:18:30,510 --> 00:18:32,400
I want to thank you on Ye Xian's behalf.

387
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:33,880
There's no need to thank me.

388
00:18:33,880 --> 00:18:35,960
Marquis Changxing
dedicated his life to military service

389
00:18:35,960 --> 00:18:37,720
and made contributions to the country.

390
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:39,160
Even if His Majesty had said nothing,

391
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:41,090
I would have found a way to save him.

392
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:42,070
Right now,

393
00:18:42,550 --> 00:18:43,510
the peace talks
with the Northern barbarians

394
00:18:43,510 --> 00:18:44,770
are still unresolved.

395
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:46,400
If the northern side were to learn

396
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:47,640
that Marquis Changxing

397
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:49,400
had been imprisoned and gravely ill—

398
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:51,240
they might start the war again.

399
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:53,270
My mentor considered this as well.

400
00:18:53,270 --> 00:18:54,550
He was afraid that Marquis Changxing

401
00:18:54,550 --> 00:18:55,740
would suddenly pass away

402
00:18:55,740 --> 00:18:57,270
before the peace talks concluded,

403
00:18:57,270 --> 00:18:59,330
so he decided to let him off this time.

404
00:19:00,070 --> 00:19:01,420
Then how serious

405
00:19:01,760 --> 00:19:03,760
is Marquis Changxing's condition?

406
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:06,130
He doesn't have much time left.

407
00:19:06,510 --> 00:19:08,590
I've managed to protect his reputation,

408
00:19:08,590 --> 00:19:10,510
but Marquis Changxing family's prestige,

409
00:19:10,510 --> 00:19:11,730
built over decades,

410
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:13,360
is difficult to sustain.

411
00:19:24,070 --> 00:19:24,790
That year,

412
00:19:26,920 --> 00:19:29,120
when I had become my mentor's disciple,

413
00:19:29,350 --> 00:19:30,720
the Yellow River flooded,

414
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:33,640
and my mentor didn't sleep
for three days and nights.

415
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:34,420
His mouth

416
00:19:34,720 --> 00:19:35,920
was full of blisters.

417
00:19:36,500 --> 00:19:39,110
I was by his side,
attending to his writing needs.

418
00:19:39,110 --> 00:19:41,270
I told him
he was pushing himself too hard,

419
00:19:41,270 --> 00:19:41,960
and he said,

420
00:19:43,290 --> 00:19:44,540
"Our suffering

421
00:19:44,790 --> 00:19:45,990
will eventually end,

422
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:48,830
but the suffering of the common people

423
00:19:48,830 --> 00:19:50,110
never does."

424
00:19:53,310 --> 00:19:54,370
But what about now?

425
00:19:55,310 --> 00:19:56,510
From the palace coup,

426
00:19:57,270 --> 00:19:59,870
to replacing disaster relief grain
with bran,

427
00:20:00,240 --> 00:20:03,100
to what happened
with Marquis Changxing's family—

428
00:20:03,680 --> 00:20:04,810
I'm afraid my mentor

429
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:09,050
has already lost his original intention.

430
00:20:22,810 --> 00:20:23,870
I remember

431
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:26,000
when I was seven,

432
00:20:27,310 --> 00:20:29,110
after the great victory at Hulan Pass,

433
00:20:29,110 --> 00:20:30,170
Marquis Changxing

434
00:20:30,400 --> 00:20:32,030
watered his horse by the Wuliang River

435
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:33,110
and composed a poem

436
00:20:34,310 --> 00:20:35,770
that became widely known:

437
00:20:38,160 --> 00:20:40,670
"Becoming a lord is not my desire,

438
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:44,510
I only wish for everlasting peace."

439
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:54,830
Becoming a lord is not my desire,

440
00:20:55,640 --> 00:20:59,880
I only wish for everlasting peace."

441
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:02,880
You are right.

442
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:40,790
Why aren't you eating?

443
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:02,320
Even if you have no appetite,

444
00:22:02,510 --> 00:22:03,910
at least drink some soup.

445
00:22:05,030 --> 00:22:05,750
I can't.

446
00:22:07,750 --> 00:22:08,750
You can't keep

447
00:22:08,750 --> 00:22:10,480
ruining your health like this.

448
00:22:10,790 --> 00:22:11,800
If you collapse,

449
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:12,960
what am I supposed to do?

450
00:22:12,960 --> 00:22:15,020
What are your parents supposed to do?

451
00:22:22,030 --> 00:22:22,890
Your Lordship,

452
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:25,110
Miss Xue sent someone over with gifts.

453
00:22:25,110 --> 00:22:25,920
Miss Xue?

454
00:22:26,510 --> 00:22:27,000
Who?

455
00:22:29,720 --> 00:22:30,440
Xue Qinglan?

456
00:22:30,440 --> 00:22:31,160
Exactly.

457
00:22:32,510 --> 00:22:33,370
Throw them out.

458
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:34,740
Your Lordship,

459
00:22:35,110 --> 00:22:36,750
there's ten-year-old ginseng

460
00:22:36,750 --> 00:22:38,030
and the finest borneol among them.

461
00:22:38,030 --> 00:22:38,700
Throw them out!

462
00:22:38,700 --> 00:22:39,430
Understood.

463
00:22:53,340 --> 00:22:56,150
[House of Virtue and Brilliance]

464
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:58,070
108 bolts of Yunjin brocade;

465
00:22:58,790 --> 00:23:01,440
18 pairs of layered filigree

466
00:23:01,440 --> 00:23:02,570
gold ruyi hairpins;

467
00:23:02,570 --> 00:23:04,080
[66,600 taels of fine silver]

468
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:04,800
and the wedding money...

469
00:23:05,830 --> 00:23:07,960
Why are there so many betrothal gifts?

470
00:23:09,160 --> 00:23:11,290
Third Brother adores his future wife.

471
00:23:11,350 --> 00:23:12,790
I showed him the draft

472
00:23:12,140 --> 00:23:15,320
[Orchid Chamber Fragrance]

473
00:23:12,790 --> 00:23:13,960
of the betrothal gift list,

474
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:15,760
and he added more items himself—

475
00:23:16,110 --> 00:23:18,400
all from his own savings,

476
00:23:18,590 --> 00:23:20,240
not the common fund.

477
00:23:21,110 --> 00:23:22,840
So I couldn't say much about it.

478
00:23:24,200 --> 00:23:25,720
He's practically giving away

479
00:23:25,720 --> 00:23:26,850
his entire fortune.

480
00:23:28,830 --> 00:23:30,880
The wedding is set on the 16th
of the second lunar month.

481
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:32,510
The Gu family sent word earlier

482
00:23:32,510 --> 00:23:34,750
that they will formally
add to the dowry the day after tomorrow.

483
00:23:34,750 --> 00:23:36,680
I didn't dare neglect the matter,

484
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:39,510
so I picked a pair
of filigree gold hairpins

485
00:23:39,510 --> 00:23:40,550
and a pair of jade bracelets.

486
00:23:40,550 --> 00:23:42,610
I'll have Sixth Sister deliver them.

487
00:23:43,270 --> 00:23:44,070
Mother,

488
00:23:44,830 --> 00:23:45,590
will you

489
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:47,350
also...

490
00:23:48,590 --> 00:23:51,590
Adding to the dowry
is the bride's family's business.

491
00:23:51,830 --> 00:23:52,880
Zhao

492
00:23:53,240 --> 00:23:54,560
is my sister's

493
00:23:54,590 --> 00:23:55,830
most beloved child.

494
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:57,940
The Ji family will certainly be generous

495
00:23:57,940 --> 00:23:59,400
with the dowry additions.

496
00:23:59,830 --> 00:24:02,030
There is no need for me to join the crowd.

497
00:24:03,440 --> 00:24:04,270
Yes.

498
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:06,400
Never mind.

499
00:24:08,030 --> 00:24:10,680
I do have a white jade ruyi here.

500
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:12,200
Take it with you,

501
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:13,730
and have Ying deliver it

502
00:24:14,070 --> 00:24:15,440
along with the rest.

503
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:19,070
Sure thing,

504
00:24:19,070 --> 00:24:20,350
my dear mother,

505
00:24:20,550 --> 00:24:23,000
I knew you were the most generous of all.

506
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:24,840
By the way.

507
00:24:25,400 --> 00:24:27,310
Second Master sent a letter yesterday,

508
00:24:27,310 --> 00:24:28,400
saying he will come

509
00:24:28,440 --> 00:24:30,440
for Third Brother's wedding banquet.

510
00:24:30,440 --> 00:24:32,200
He should be leaving soon.

511
00:24:33,030 --> 00:24:35,160
I've also sent a letter to Xuanqing,

512
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:37,420
asking him to return as soon as possible.

513
00:24:40,480 --> 00:24:41,750
What's wrong, Mother?

514
00:24:42,310 --> 00:24:44,370
She’s about to marry into the family,

515
00:24:44,590 --> 00:24:45,960
and you still haven't

516
00:24:46,030 --> 00:24:47,270
gotten over it?

517
00:24:47,650 --> 00:24:49,590
You saw right through me.

518
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:52,720
To be honest,

519
00:24:54,510 --> 00:24:56,750
I'm truly unhappy about it.

520
00:24:57,830 --> 00:24:59,160
Mother,

521
00:24:59,550 --> 00:25:02,550
Third Brother has risen rapidly
these past few years,

522
00:25:02,590 --> 00:25:04,160
holding high positions and great power.

523
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:05,030
At court,

524
00:25:05,030 --> 00:25:06,740
he's used to having the final say.

525
00:25:06,740 --> 00:25:10,520
[Orchid Chamber Fragrance]

526
00:25:07,440 --> 00:25:08,510
So when he returns home,

527
00:25:08,510 --> 00:25:10,680
he naturally isn't accustomed
to being told what to do.

528
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:12,000
Besides,

529
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:13,960
Old Madam Ji

530
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:16,500
also just found out about it, didn't she?

531
00:25:17,310 --> 00:25:19,110
But to put it bluntly,

532
00:25:19,790 --> 00:25:21,520
there's indeed some suspicion

533
00:25:21,790 --> 00:25:23,350
that he and Miss Gu

534
00:25:24,590 --> 00:25:26,830
were privately involved
before the engagement.

535
00:25:26,830 --> 00:25:29,510
You call that merely a suspicion?

536
00:25:35,520 --> 00:25:40,560
[Thrice Reflections Against Greed;
Ninefold Virtues in the Sound of the Qin]

537
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:37,310
Send this over for her dowry ceremony

538
00:25:37,310 --> 00:25:38,640
the day after tomorrow.

539
00:25:45,830 --> 00:25:47,070
I was taking a nap,

540
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:48,830
and you called me over so urgently

541
00:25:48,830 --> 00:25:50,360
just to deliver something?

542
00:25:50,440 --> 00:25:51,200
Besides,

543
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:53,110
Jinzhao is already so wealthy.

544
00:25:53,240 --> 00:25:53,790
Does she really need you

545
00:25:53,790 --> 00:25:55,000
to add to her dowry?

546
00:25:55,510 --> 00:25:57,790
Whether she's rich or not is her business.

547
00:25:57,790 --> 00:25:59,800
Adding to her dowry is simply my gesture.

548
00:25:59,800 --> 00:26:01,330
Hurry and deliver it for me.

549
00:26:06,270 --> 00:26:07,240
Don't worry.

550
00:26:09,590 --> 00:26:10,110
Look.

551
00:26:10,830 --> 00:26:12,110
This one is for you.

552
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:17,440
Do you like it?

553
00:26:21,510 --> 00:26:22,070
Alright.

554
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:23,640
I'll deliver it for you.

555
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:43,640
Your ink bamboo painting

556
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:45,110
is getting better and better.

557
00:26:45,110 --> 00:26:46,000
At first glance,

558
00:26:46,000 --> 00:26:48,260
I thought it was painted by Third Master.

559
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:53,680
Third Uncle's ink bamboo has

560
00:26:53,960 --> 00:26:55,240
such elegance and depth.

561
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:56,550
How could I possibly compare to him?

562
00:26:56,550 --> 00:26:57,810
You're far too modest.

563
00:26:58,110 --> 00:26:59,720
Third Master is indeed exceptional,

564
00:26:59,720 --> 00:27:01,920
but you also passed the exam as a Tanhua.

565
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:02,920
You aren't

566
00:27:03,110 --> 00:27:04,240
far behind him.

567
00:27:04,550 --> 00:27:05,010
Go away.

568
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:07,680
All you know is how to flatter me.

569
00:27:11,350 --> 00:27:13,210
My Lord, there's a letter for you.

570
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:30,750
It's from my youngest aunt.

571
00:27:30,750 --> 00:27:34,150
She probably wants to know
when you'll arrive in the capital.

572
00:27:42,650 --> 00:27:44,480
[Gu Mansion]

573
00:27:48,140 --> 00:27:50,130
[Gu]

574
00:27:49,030 --> 00:27:50,690
These are all for Miss Gu's dowry.

575
00:27:50,690 --> 00:27:52,090
Not just the Ji family...

576
00:27:52,880 --> 00:27:53,510
Welcome, Madam Liu.

577
00:27:53,510 --> 00:27:54,680
and the Chen family too.

578
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:56,000
They said after Old Madam
saw

579
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:57,070
the Chen family's list of betrothal gifts,

580
00:27:57,070 --> 00:27:58,310
she immediately had an empty storeroom

581
00:27:58,310 --> 00:27:59,200
cleared out to place the gifts.

582
00:27:59,200 --> 00:28:00,130
Welcome, Madam Wang.

583
00:27:59,660 --> 00:28:02,510
[Gu]

584
00:28:12,350 --> 00:28:13,160
Zhao.

585
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:16,490
Lian caught a cold last night.

586
00:28:16,790 --> 00:28:17,440
Early this morning,

587
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:19,240
a physician wrote a prescription for her,

588
00:28:19,240 --> 00:28:20,760
so I told her not to come,

589
00:28:20,830 --> 00:28:22,490
in case she passed it on to you.

590
00:28:24,030 --> 00:28:24,920
This

591
00:28:26,720 --> 00:28:28,400
is her gift for your dowry.

592
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:32,240
And these

593
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:34,790
are from me.

594
00:28:35,030 --> 00:28:36,760
I only wish that, in the future,

595
00:28:36,790 --> 00:28:39,310
everything will go exactly as you wish.

596
00:28:40,200 --> 00:28:41,530
Thank you, Second Aunt.

597
00:28:50,110 --> 00:28:51,550
My Lady, Mrs. Mu is here.

598
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:53,720
I see.

599
00:28:55,440 --> 00:28:56,790
Which Mrs. Mu?

600
00:28:57,640 --> 00:28:59,200
The wife of Lord Mu Shi'an.

601
00:29:01,030 --> 00:29:03,920
The newly appointed
Vice Minister of Personnel?

602
00:29:05,310 --> 00:29:07,270
Your Second Uncle didn't get the post,

603
00:29:07,270 --> 00:29:08,830
and neither did Yao Ping,

604
00:29:09,160 --> 00:29:11,160
yet he ended up benefiting instead.

605
00:29:12,310 --> 00:29:14,640
I'll go with you to take a look.

606
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:16,640
After you.

607
00:29:23,590 --> 00:29:24,790
Greetings, Mrs. Mu.

608
00:29:26,240 --> 00:29:27,410
My Master

609
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:29,810
has been friends with Lord Chen for years.

610
00:29:29,920 --> 00:29:30,590
This time,

611
00:29:30,750 --> 00:29:32,510
when we heard about this splendid match,

612
00:29:32,510 --> 00:29:34,570
we were both truly delighted for him.

613
00:29:34,790 --> 00:29:36,720
Look at this beautiful face.

614
00:29:34,920 --> 00:29:37,700
[Mrs. Mu, Mu Shian's wife]

615
00:29:37,200 --> 00:29:39,530
You and Lord Chen

616
00:29:39,750 --> 00:29:41,550
are truly a match made in heaven.

617
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:43,300
You're being so kind, Mrs. Mu.

618
00:29:46,960 --> 00:29:47,960
Lan, you're here.

619
00:29:48,270 --> 00:29:48,880
Mrs. Mu,

620
00:29:48,900 --> 00:29:50,660
this is my third sister, Lan.

621
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:52,030
This is Mrs. Mu.

622
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:56,260
Greetings, Second Aunt and Zhao.

623
00:29:57,640 --> 00:29:58,770
Greetings, Mrs. Mu.

624
00:30:00,790 --> 00:30:01,880
So you are Lan.

625
00:30:02,790 --> 00:30:03,400
Yes.

626
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:08,030
Zhao,

627
00:30:08,310 --> 00:30:08,920
I didn't have

628
00:30:08,920 --> 00:30:10,310
anything worthy of giving,

629
00:30:10,310 --> 00:30:12,020
so I sewed a wedding quilt

630
00:30:12,110 --> 00:30:13,340
for you.

631
00:30:13,590 --> 00:30:14,750
Something made with your own hands

632
00:30:14,750 --> 00:30:16,610
is worth more than gold or silver.

633
00:30:17,590 --> 00:30:18,510
The embroidery

634
00:30:18,720 --> 00:30:20,350
is really something!

635
00:30:20,640 --> 00:30:22,500
Did you embroider this yourself?

636
00:30:22,550 --> 00:30:23,200
Yes.

637
00:30:24,510 --> 00:30:26,960
What a wonderful needlework!

638
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:32,310
I'll pack the wedding quilt
into the chest.

639
00:30:32,310 --> 00:30:32,790
Okay.

640
00:30:34,590 --> 00:30:35,270
Miss Gu,

641
00:30:35,720 --> 00:30:37,980
the Sixth Miss of the Chen family is here.

642
00:30:39,550 --> 00:30:41,880
Someone from the Chen family came as well?

643
00:30:42,590 --> 00:30:43,720
I'll go welcome her.

644
00:30:51,350 --> 00:30:52,200
Yanying,

645
00:30:52,250 --> 00:30:52,930
I thought

646
00:30:52,960 --> 00:30:54,420
you weren't coming today.

647
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:55,640
I didn't want to come.

648
00:30:56,160 --> 00:30:58,000
But someone was worried
you'd feel slighted,

649
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:58,870
so he insisted I come over

650
00:30:58,870 --> 00:31:00,400
to deliver gifts for your dowry day.

651
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:02,330
My dear sister, it's my fault.

652
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:03,880
I shouldn't have kept it from you.

653
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:05,110
Since you know you were wrong,

654
00:31:05,110 --> 00:31:06,030
let me ask you something.

655
00:31:06,030 --> 00:31:07,030
At your coming-of-age ceremony,

656
00:31:07,030 --> 00:31:08,230
Yanyun was there too.

657
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:09,110
Was that when the two of you

658
00:31:09,110 --> 00:31:10,400
start seeing each other?

659
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:11,440
Of course not.

660
00:31:11,960 --> 00:31:13,960
What about the Mid-Autumn Festival

661
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:16,060
when we admired the chrysanthemums?

662
00:31:16,110 --> 00:31:17,680
I don't think so.

663
00:31:18,750 --> 00:31:20,030
Then when was it?

664
00:31:20,750 --> 00:31:23,950
It couldn't possibly be
during the Spring Outing, right?

665
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:26,790
Wait, I know!

666
00:31:27,070 --> 00:31:28,180
Was it in Tongzhou?

667
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:29,640
I remember two years ago,

668
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:31,200
Yanyun was in Tongzhou for a long time.

669
00:31:31,200 --> 00:31:32,600
Were you in Tongzhou too?

670
00:31:34,590 --> 00:31:35,590
Come with me.

671
00:31:41,310 --> 00:31:42,750
I'm not done asking questions yet.

672
00:31:42,750 --> 00:31:44,350
Don't think you can bribe me.

673
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:50,720
These were carved

674
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:52,350
by the best craftsman in Jiangnan.

675
00:31:52,350 --> 00:31:53,550
There are 12 in total.

676
00:31:53,640 --> 00:31:55,400
Each one has a different shape.

677
00:31:56,510 --> 00:31:58,010
What are you doing?

678
00:31:58,200 --> 00:31:59,200
As long as you promise me

679
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:00,720
not to ask any more questions,

680
00:32:00,720 --> 00:32:01,730
and I'll give you

681
00:32:01,790 --> 00:32:02,720
all of these.

682
00:32:06,550 --> 00:32:07,920
How could you do this?

683
00:32:09,350 --> 00:32:10,440
There's also a set of eight

684
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:11,350
jade puppies.

685
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:16,920
I came here to deliver gifts

686
00:32:16,920 --> 00:32:18,070
for your dowry.

687
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:18,880
Why are you giving me

688
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:20,240
gifts instead?

689
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:23,440
And there are also four little jade boys.

690
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:24,960
If you wind up the mechanism,

691
00:32:24,960 --> 00:32:26,220
they can even do flips.

692
00:32:28,200 --> 00:32:29,070
Greetings, Third Sister-in-law!

693
00:32:29,070 --> 00:32:30,590
I suddenly don't want to ask anything.

694
00:32:30,590 --> 00:32:32,520
As long as you and Yanyun are happy.

695
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:39,350
Miss Yu is here.

696
00:32:43,050 --> 00:32:51,550
[Generations of Excellence]

697
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:47,030
Wanxue.

698
00:32:50,400 --> 00:32:51,600
What took you so long?

699
00:32:51,640 --> 00:32:53,300
The banquet is about to start.

700
00:32:53,480 --> 00:32:54,880
I had no choice.

701
00:32:54,880 --> 00:32:56,340
I was going to leave early,

702
00:32:56,480 --> 00:32:58,110
but my stepmother suddenly said
she had a headache.

703
00:32:58,110 --> 00:32:59,570
I almost couldn't leave.

704
00:32:59,680 --> 00:33:01,880
Luckily, Father came and helped me out.

705
00:33:02,510 --> 00:33:03,590
I don't have anything especially fine

706
00:33:03,590 --> 00:33:04,590
to give you, Zhao.

707
00:33:06,030 --> 00:33:08,560
This box contains
the latest eyebrow powder.

708
00:33:09,270 --> 00:33:10,310
And this

709
00:33:10,310 --> 00:33:11,110
is the scented powder I made myself—

710
00:33:11,110 --> 00:33:13,350
it's better than what you can buy outside.

711
00:33:13,350 --> 00:33:14,790
And here is a box of silver ingots

712
00:33:14,790 --> 00:33:16,790
for you to reward the servants with.

713
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:18,480
They're all great and very useful.

714
00:33:18,480 --> 00:33:19,350
I like them all.

715
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:21,510
Hold on.

716
00:33:21,720 --> 00:33:23,400
You're engaged to Xuanqing now.

717
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:24,310
You shouldn't call her Zhao anymore,

718
00:33:24,310 --> 00:33:26,170
instead you should call her Aunt,

719
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:27,550
And you shouldn't call her Wanxue either—

720
00:33:27,550 --> 00:33:29,480
you should call her Niece-in-law.

721
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:32,590
I thought about it all night yesterday,

722
00:33:32,590 --> 00:33:34,440
whether I should call you Zhao

723
00:33:34,510 --> 00:33:35,550
or Aunt.

724
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:36,440
But in the end,

725
00:33:36,550 --> 00:33:37,880
I still called you Zhao.

726
00:33:38,070 --> 00:33:40,450
I really couldn't call you Aunt.

727
00:33:42,030 --> 00:33:43,390
Just call me Zhao.

728
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:45,310
Don't worry about the seniority.

729
00:33:45,310 --> 00:33:47,000
You two might be willing
to keep it that way,

730
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:48,070
but I'm certainly not.

731
00:33:48,070 --> 00:33:49,510
Come here, my dear niece-in-law.

732
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:51,170
Give your Aunt a shoulder rub.

733
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:53,640
Give you an inch and you take a mile!

734
00:33:53,790 --> 00:33:54,960
I'm not talking to you.

735
00:33:54,960 --> 00:33:56,490
I'm going to put these away.

736
00:34:02,310 --> 00:34:03,680
She's shy.

737
00:34:03,960 --> 00:34:04,750
Look at you.

738
00:34:04,750 --> 00:34:06,160
I'm not talking to you either.

739
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:07,310
I'll go prepare the banquet.

740
00:34:07,310 --> 00:34:08,110
Are you coming with me?

741
00:34:08,110 --> 00:34:12,780
[Generations of Excellence]

742
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:09,449
Let's go.

743
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:28,540
Just place it behind that box.

744
00:34:39,710 --> 00:34:40,280
My Lady.

745
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:42,300
Since Miss Ying is also here today,

746
00:34:42,300 --> 00:34:43,670
why don't you ask her

747
00:34:43,840 --> 00:34:45,710
about your marriage to Young Master Chen

748
00:34:45,710 --> 00:34:48,239
and what exactly
the Chen family is planning?

749
00:34:49,110 --> 00:34:50,239
How could I possibly

750
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:51,710
be the one to ask?

751
00:34:51,920 --> 00:34:52,760
But, My Lady,

752
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:54,000
the Chen family scheduled the wedding

753
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:55,340
for the end of last year.

754
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:56,510
Then, out of nowhere, Young Master Chen

755
00:34:56,510 --> 00:34:57,400
suddenly went to Shanxi for peace talks

756
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:58,800
with the northern barbarians.

757
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:00,110
Forgive me for speaking bluntly,

758
00:35:00,110 --> 00:35:00,800
since he already
had a marriage arrangement,

759
00:35:00,800 --> 00:35:02,110
why would he accept such an assignment?

760
00:35:02,110 --> 00:35:03,170
If it were anyone else,

761
00:35:03,170 --> 00:35:04,150
naturally they couldn't refuse

762
00:35:04,150 --> 00:35:05,320
an order from the Imperial Court.

763
00:35:05,320 --> 00:35:06,000
But Young Master Chen

764
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,280
is Lord Chen's own nephew—

765
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:07,920
going or staying

766
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:08,590
was entirely up to one word

767
00:35:08,590 --> 00:35:10,030
-from Lord Chen.
-Enough.

768
00:35:10,030 --> 00:35:11,710
I've clearly spoiled you too much.

769
00:35:11,710 --> 00:35:13,970
You're speaking completely out of line.

770
00:35:16,010 --> 00:35:22,330
[Chen Mansion]

771
00:35:48,290 --> 00:35:52,330
[Orchid Chamber Fragrance]

772
00:35:49,190 --> 00:35:50,080
Mother.

773
00:35:50,150 --> 00:35:51,070
Xuanqing

774
00:35:51,150 --> 00:35:53,110
has truly grown into a fine,

775
00:35:53,230 --> 00:35:54,360
accomplished man.

776
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:56,760
Honestly,

777
00:35:56,760 --> 00:35:58,400
the mansion feels so empty without you

778
00:35:58,400 --> 00:36:00,460
around to liven things up.

779
00:36:03,440 --> 00:36:04,360
Xuanqing.

780
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:05,760
Xuanqing?

781
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:09,960
Xuanqing.

782
00:36:13,070 --> 00:36:13,800
Second Aunt.

783
00:36:14,510 --> 00:36:15,970
I was distracted just now.

784
00:36:16,030 --> 00:36:17,030
What were you saying?

785
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:21,890
[Orchid Chamber Fragrance]

786
00:36:17,590 --> 00:36:19,510
Oh, nothing much.

787
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:20,670
I was just saying

788
00:36:20,670 --> 00:36:22,670
you've truly become an accomplished man.

789
00:36:22,670 --> 00:36:24,410
When I walked in just now

790
00:36:24,440 --> 00:36:25,880
and saw you sitting there,

791
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:27,070
for a moment

792
00:36:27,190 --> 00:36:27,760
I thought

793
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:29,640
I was looking at your Third Uncle.

794
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:33,570
It's a long and exhausting journey

795
00:36:33,630 --> 00:36:35,320
back from Shanxi.

796
00:36:35,440 --> 00:36:37,020
You must be very tired.

797
00:36:37,070 --> 00:36:39,110
Hurry back and get some rest.

798
00:36:45,150 --> 00:36:46,550
Thank you, Grandmother.

799
00:36:47,440 --> 00:36:49,500
I have something to discuss with you.

800
00:36:49,630 --> 00:36:51,320
I've been in Shanxi for half a year,

801
00:36:51,320 --> 00:36:53,580
and there is still much unfinished work.

802
00:36:53,920 --> 00:36:55,000
I was thinking

803
00:36:55,280 --> 00:36:57,030
of moving into the Hanlin Academy
quarters tomorrow,

804
00:36:57,030 --> 00:36:59,230
and returning after the offices close.

805
00:36:59,550 --> 00:37:01,800
How busy can the Hanlin Academy be?

806
00:37:02,320 --> 00:37:03,150
Don't carry

807
00:37:03,150 --> 00:37:05,480
the weight of the world on your shoulders.

808
00:37:05,510 --> 00:37:08,310
Rest for a few days

809
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:10,640
before taking on your next assignment.

810
00:37:11,630 --> 00:37:12,630
Besides,

811
00:37:13,500 --> 00:37:14,630
in a few days,

812
00:37:15,070 --> 00:37:17,510
your Third Uncle is getting married.

813
00:37:18,190 --> 00:37:19,960
You can return to work

814
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:22,280
after attending the wedding banquet.

815
00:37:22,570 --> 00:37:25,130
[Orchid Chamber Fragrance]

816
00:37:23,230 --> 00:37:23,810
Right,

817
00:37:24,150 --> 00:37:25,880
don't forget about the Yu family.

818
00:37:25,880 --> 00:37:27,280
Now that you're back,

819
00:37:27,590 --> 00:37:29,000
remember to

820
00:37:29,230 --> 00:37:31,670
visit your future in-laws early,

821
00:37:32,280 --> 00:37:34,230
so they won't find fault with you.

822
00:37:39,170 --> 00:37:40,840
Yes, Grandmother.

823
00:38:07,660 --> 00:38:09,250
♪ Once I wrote of spring and fall ♪

824
00:38:10,050 --> 00:38:12,920
♪ Yet fell through time's abyss ♪

825
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:16,560
♪ Every shade turned bitter ♪

826
00:38:17,470 --> 00:38:20,220
♪ Every longing became sorrow ♪

827
00:38:22,940 --> 00:38:24,410
♪ I've seen through right and wrong ♪

828
00:38:25,410 --> 00:38:30,130
[Shunning the World, Returning to Nature]

829
00:38:25,630 --> 00:38:28,650
♪ Old vows washed away like ash ♪

830
00:38:29,730 --> 00:38:35,990
♪ True devotion is knowing
the freedom within your heart♪

831
00:38:36,780 --> 00:38:39,690
♪ Word by word, hand in hand ♪

832
00:38:40,640 --> 00:38:43,370
♪ My heart grows cold like rust ♪

833
00:38:44,400 --> 00:38:47,400
♪ The stars send you far away ♪

834
00:38:48,240 --> 00:38:50,650
♪ Yet one thought still remains ♪

835
00:38:48,670 --> 00:38:49,360
Now you know

836
00:38:49,360 --> 00:38:50,560
the so-called truth.

837
00:38:51,940 --> 00:38:53,330
Whether to get married to the Yu family

838
00:38:52,290 --> 00:38:55,210
♪ You share bright days with another ♪

839
00:38:54,360 --> 00:38:54,960
and try to keep this secret

840
00:38:54,960 --> 00:38:56,050
as tightly as possible,

841
00:38:56,050 --> 00:38:59,130
♪ I walk with my lonely shadow ♪

842
00:38:57,550 --> 00:38:58,950
or to give up the marriage

843
00:38:59,890 --> 00:39:07,140
♪ Filling every broken fold
with memories of us ♪

844
00:39:00,400 --> 00:39:02,070
and prepare to face everything

845
00:39:02,070 --> 00:39:03,870
after you pass the examination—

846
00:39:04,620 --> 00:39:05,750
the choice is yours.

847
00:39:24,850 --> 00:39:26,460
♪ We once drank to talk of love and hate ♪

848
00:39:27,750 --> 00:39:30,130
♪ But we fell into
the deep ditch of rumors ♪

849
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:34,200
♪ Meeting and parting were like
moves on a chessboard ♪

850
00:39:34,860 --> 00:39:37,860
♪ Every heartfelt word ended as a fault ♪

851
00:39:40,400 --> 00:39:41,910
♪ Seen the sun rise and the moon set ♪

852
00:39:43,150 --> 00:39:45,640
♪ Only sigh that we are no longer
on the same path ♪

853
00:39:46,950 --> 00:39:53,640
♪ One wrong choice drove
my old friend away like a drifting bird ♪

854
00:39:54,260 --> 00:39:57,350
♪ With every step, I look back ♪

855
00:39:58,100 --> 00:40:00,590
♪ My heart grows cold like rust ♪

856
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:04,870
♪ The stars send you far away ♪

857
00:40:05,840 --> 00:40:08,260
♪ Yet one thought still remains ♪

858
00:40:09,770 --> 00:40:12,840
♪ You share bright days with another ♪

859
00:40:10,670 --> 00:40:11,280
Yunting.

860
00:40:13,770 --> 00:40:16,500
♪ I walk with my lonely shadow ♪

861
00:40:17,660 --> 00:40:24,590
♪ Filling every broken fold
with memories of us ♪

862
00:40:18,670 --> 00:40:19,950
Deliver this letter

863
00:40:20,030 --> 00:40:21,280
to Miss Gu for me.

864
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,610
This is inappropriate!

865
00:40:23,910 --> 00:40:25,680
I just want to see her.

866
00:40:26,670 --> 00:40:28,590
What's inappropriate about that?

867
00:40:28,590 --> 00:40:29,720
I just want to ask her

868
00:40:30,230 --> 00:40:32,030
why she agreed to this marriage.

869
00:40:32,150 --> 00:40:34,000
Does she have some hidden troubles?

870
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:35,960
Young Master, it's really inappropriate!

871
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:37,690
What if Third Master finds out?

872
00:40:40,750 --> 00:40:43,620
♪ With every step, I look back ♪

873
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,000
If you are afraid,

874
00:40:43,150 --> 00:40:44,150
I will deliver it myself.

875
00:40:44,150 --> 00:40:44,920
No, no!

876
00:40:44,450 --> 00:40:46,570
♪ My heart grows cold like rust ♪

877
00:40:45,880 --> 00:40:46,680
Please don't.

878
00:40:48,110 --> 00:40:48,880
Fine.

879
00:40:48,570 --> 00:40:51,290
♪ The stars send you far away ♪

880
00:40:49,550 --> 00:40:50,810
I'll go deliver it now.

881
00:40:52,410 --> 00:40:55,070
♪ Yet one thought still remains ♪

882
00:40:56,230 --> 00:40:56,710
Go now.

883
00:40:56,800 --> 00:40:59,310
♪ You share bright days with another ♪

884
00:41:00,060 --> 00:41:03,090
♪ I walk with my lonely shadow ♪

885
00:41:03,980 --> 00:41:09,930
♪ Filling every broken fold
with memories of us ♪

886
00:41:11,870 --> 00:41:17,630
♪ Filling every broken fold
with memories of us ♪

887
00:41:13,710 --> 00:41:14,230
My Lady.

888
00:41:16,710 --> 00:41:17,510
This is the dowry gift

889
00:41:17,510 --> 00:41:18,500
from Madam.

890
00:41:18,710 --> 00:41:19,510
Madam said

891
00:41:19,510 --> 00:41:20,030
she has been staying at the mansion

892
00:41:20,030 --> 00:41:21,920
taking care of the Marquis these days.

893
00:41:21,920 --> 00:41:23,150
She can't get the medicine smell off her,

894
00:41:23,150 --> 00:41:24,300
so she won't come personally

895
00:41:24,300 --> 00:41:25,500
to congratulate you.

896
00:41:26,030 --> 00:41:27,760
Please give Fifth Aunt my thanks,

897
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:29,690
and send my regards to the Marquis.

898
00:41:30,150 --> 00:41:31,210
Thank you, My Lady.

899
00:41:40,590 --> 00:41:41,150
My Lady.

900
00:41:44,230 --> 00:41:44,840
This...

901
00:41:47,710 --> 00:41:48,770
Whose letter is it?

902
00:41:53,710 --> 00:41:55,800
It's from Young Master Chen's servant,

903
00:41:55,430 --> 00:41:56,880
[Respectfully Presented to Jinzhao]

904
00:41:55,800 --> 00:41:56,800
Yunting.

905
00:41:58,150 --> 00:41:59,150
He also said

906
00:41:59,510 --> 00:42:00,670
that Young Master Chen,

907
00:42:00,670 --> 00:42:02,070
has lost his appetite for days,

908
00:42:02,070 --> 00:42:03,930
because you are getting married.

909
00:42:06,730 --> 00:42:08,120
[Respectfully Presented to Jinzhao]

910
00:42:08,880 --> 00:42:09,670
My Lady, aren't you going to read

911
00:42:09,670 --> 00:42:10,630
what's written inside?

912
00:42:10,630 --> 00:42:11,190
No need.

913
00:42:11,710 --> 00:42:12,510
Even if I read it,

914
00:42:12,510 --> 00:42:14,150
there's nothing I can do for him.

915
00:42:14,150 --> 00:42:15,630
It would only upset me.

916
00:42:16,710 --> 00:42:17,400
Indeed.

917
00:42:18,340 --> 00:42:22,620
[Respectfully Presented to Jinzhao]

918
00:42:19,110 --> 00:42:20,070
It was clearly Young Master Chen

919
00:42:20,070 --> 00:42:21,510
who broke his promise first,

920
00:42:21,510 --> 00:42:22,360
yet now he acts

921
00:42:23,510 --> 00:42:25,240
as if he's the heartbroken one.

922
00:42:27,800 --> 00:42:28,400
By the way,

923
00:42:28,590 --> 00:42:29,960
if Yunting hasn't gone far yet,

924
00:42:29,960 --> 00:42:30,710
catch up to him

925
00:42:30,710 --> 00:42:32,240
and pass on a message for me.

926
00:42:32,480 --> 00:42:34,150
Tell him to inform his master

927
00:42:34,280 --> 00:42:36,280
to eat well and take care of himself.

928
00:42:37,150 --> 00:42:38,550
I moved on a long time ago,

929
00:42:38,550 --> 00:42:39,950
and he should do the same.

930
00:42:46,060 --> 00:42:48,420
[Respectfully Presented to Jinzhao]

931
00:43:02,440 --> 00:43:06,230
[A Splendid Match]
